      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the doctor but i'm trying to avoid the hassle right now. if i'm just dealing with side effects, would drinking way more water help balance it out or is that something i shouldn't mess with? i've heard people say hydration is key for lithium so i was thinking of just doubling my water intake to see if that fixes the nausea.",
